  Gabriel had many wounds. Magnus saw this and contacted Kit Kat.."We have a 
hurt bot here. May we use your cr chamber?"
  Gabriel looked up almost a shock on his face."Did you say Kit Kat?'
 "Yes " magnus said intriqued.
   "I must see her. She is important to what has happened. My world rests on 
her."
  Magnus did not say a word. They strated for the pred base. Before they left 
Magnus told the troops at the ark.."Clear out remains of the ark. And make a 
pile of useful and not useful patrs." he flew off with gabriel over his 
shoulder.
